  "key": "C minor",
  "genre": [
    "Alternative",
    "Indie"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 6,
  "lyrics": "Shut it out, dude, shut it out, shut it out. Mess it up. I just wanna start this off by saying you're my friend, you're my friend. I know I pushed a little hard at the beginning and found myself within that hemisphere. But I know that there's more to grow and sometimes I let fear take the wheel and steer. Like the incubus line I feel in time, yeah. Sometimes the dark hits your window and you can't find where the crack begins. Then you think you're not good enough for you and me and, yeah. Seems I've been singing a little slower. Seems I've been not repping the potential that could be me. But it can't be the thing that I was guided to do. I need to feel you, yeah. I need to feel like it's true, it's true. I need to feel you, yeah, feel you really. And I need to know if it's true. Cause I ain't trying to do what the other people do and do and do unto others as you would say you do unto yourself but you never do. Selfish grind and gratitude leaves us all alone. If I knew the way to tell you that I could be the spark of it all for me, then I would have done it by now, can't you see? I'm here for broken and you're broken so stop trying to hurt me. I'm here for you from the beginning to the ending and now you took over my space. It wasn't for you but now you get it in a way. Be there for me or start dragging me through the mud. Respect this or just go along with the others. I'm here for you but you don't want to be here for me. What's the deal, boo?",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 3,
      "text": "Shut it out, dude, shut it out, shut it out. Mess it up.",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 36.36000061035156,
      "text": "I just wanna start this off by saying you're my friend, you're my friend.",
      "start": 30
    },
    {
      "end": 44.540000915527344,
      "text": "I know I pushed a little hard at the beginning and found myself within that hemisphere.",
      "start": 37.380001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 52.81999969482422,
      "text": "But I know that there's more to grow and sometimes I let fear take the wheel and steer.",
      "start": 45.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 59.29999923706055,
      "text": "Like the incubus line I feel in time, yeah.",
      "start": 54.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 66.66000366210938,
      "text": "Sometimes the dark hits your window and you can't find where the crack begins.",
      "start": 59.29999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 74.66000366210938,
      "text": "Then you think you're not good enough for you and me and, yeah.",
      "start": 67.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 83,
      "text": "Seems I've been singing a little slower. Seems I've been not repping the potential that could be me.",
      "start": 74.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 87.5999984741211,
      "text": "But it can't be the thing that I was guided to do.",
      "start": 83
    },
    {
      "end": 95.83999633789062,
      "text": "I need to feel you, yeah.",
      "start": 89.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 102.68000030517578,
      "text": "I need to feel like it's true, it's true.",
      "start": 96.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 109.86000061035156,
      "text": "I need to feel you, yeah, feel you really.",
      "start": 103.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 113.80000305175781,
      "text": "And I need to know if it's true.",
      "start": 110
    },
    {
      "end": 124.54000091552734,
      "text": "Cause I ain't trying to do what the other people do and do and do unto others as you would say you do unto yourself but you never do.",
      "start": 113.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 132.3000030517578,
      "text": "Selfish grind and gratitude leaves us all alone.",
      "start": 126.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 140.75999450683594,
      "text": "If I knew the way to tell you that I could be the spark of it all for me,",
      "start": 132.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 144.4600067138672,
      "text": "then I would have done it by now, can't you see?",
      "start": 140.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 153.60000610351562,
      "text": "I'm here for broken and you're broken so stop trying to hurt me.",
      "start": 144.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 158.66000366210938,
      "text": "I'm here for you from the beginning to the ending and now you took over my space.",
      "start": 153.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 162.25999450683594,
      "text": "It wasn't for you but now you get it in a way.",
      "start": 158.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 166.24000549316406,
      "text": "Be there for me or start dragging me through the mud.",
      "start": 162.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 169.89999389648438,
      "text": "Respect this or just go along with the others.",
      "start": 166.24000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 175.8800048828125,
      "text": "I'm here for you but you don't want to be here for me.",
      "start": 170.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 177.4600067138672,
      "text": "What's the deal, boo?",
      "start": 176.22000122070312
    }
  ],
